{"tid":1446393,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"銅鑼灣大敗 但文宣可以將警狗一軍","createTime":"2019-08-11T14:58:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T17:25:32.000Z","uid":17024,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f02a529f4b692110b32dfd44a6599d52d07c4f9b","tid":1446393,"uid":17024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:58:22.000Z","msg":"聽講衝立法會、氣油彈、磚同鐵馬都係扮示威者嘅警狗做<br />\n<br />\n佢地一直潛入就係想插贓嫁禍令民意逆轉<br />\n可惜一直不成功，反而民怨更深<br />\n今日決定用內（假示威者）同外（速龍）想將前線一網打盡<br />\n無晒前線，得番和理非嘅人就唔會敢出去集會同遊行<br />\n文宣係時候做野<br />\n<br />\n今日前線死晒咁濟<br />\n希望剩低嘅勇武同和理非爭番啖氣<br />\n大家加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79afffe5dbfd05cecc6c0520ddf457d343f61691","tid":1446393,"uid":17024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:58:32.000Z","msg":"香港加油"},{"pid":"c5095c881cd7f38dfd27c58727d346c59b856ee7","tid":1446393,"uid":17024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:00:03.000Z","msg":"香港加油"},{"pid":"46aacb6cd96d95134fd4389c066faf2bdaf5adaa","tid":1446393,"uid":17024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:00:44.000Z","msg":"大家唔好放棄"},{"pid":"4e7b86a55334da9e9f5f16bc74e470213b3cd851","tid":1446393,"uid":90328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:01:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5VFtb9Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5VFtb9Z.jpg&h=d1670806&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3e3af1923fa862a3fb12581357c5f440f3ea2589","tid":1446393,"uid":170297,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:01:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果警察臥底丟磚丟汽油彈,所以狗就可以射布袋彈,咁個女仔隻眼邊個還俾佢!?</span></span>"},{"pid":"e55bb47053517bb07be1c1244b83b12880302b79","tid":1446393,"uid":174207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e7b86a55334da9e9f5f16bc74e470213b3cd851","tid":1446393,"uid":90328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":